'''三(2-苯基吡啶)铱'''是一种[[有机铱化合物|有机铱化合物]]，化学式为Ir(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>-C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>N)<sub>3</sub>，或简写为Ir(ppy)<sub>3</sub>]。它是黄绿色的固体，由Ir<sup>3+</sup>和{{le|2-苯基吡啶|2-Phenylpyridine}}阴离子构成，具有[[电致发光|电致发光]]（绿光）特性。它可由2-苯基吡啶和[[三氯化铱|三氯化铱]]的反应制得：<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1021/ic0008969|title=Synthesis and Characterization of Phosphorescent Cyclometalated Iridium Complexes|year=2001|last1=Lamansky|first1= Sergey|last2=Djurovich|first2=Peter|last3=Murphy|first3=Drew|last4=Abdel-Razzaq|first4=Feras|last5=Kwong|first5=Raymond|last6=Tsyba|first6=Irina|last7= Bortz|first7=Manfred|last8=Mui|first8=Becky|last9=Bau|first9=Robert|last10=Thompson|first10=Mark E.|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=40|issue=7|pages=1704–1711|pmid=11261983}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1021/ic00008a003|title=A new synthetic route to the preparation of a series of strong photoreducing agents: Fac-tris-ortho-metalated complexes of iridium(III) with substituted 2-phenylpyridines|year=1991|last1=Dedeian|first1=K.|last2=Djurovich|first2=P. I.|last3=Garces|first3=F. O.|last4=Carlson|first4=G.|last5=Watts|first5=R. J.|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=30|issue=8|pages=1685–1687}}</ref>
:IrCl<sub>3</sub>  + 3{{nbsp}}C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>-C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>N  →  Ir(C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>-C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>N)<sub>3</sub>  +  3 HCl

